These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee, almond-milk
1. the colombian is the fan of techno##1
2. the indonesian is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the colombian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | photography   | video-games  | magic-tricks  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Beverage     | almond-milk  | iced-tea       | hot-chocolate    | coffee     |

