.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different games are played: domino, whist, go, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea, balloon-flower, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person playing go and the person who growszinnia##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is between the person watching western movies and the person playing backgammon##2
7. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Game           | backgammon      | go       | whist      | domino       |
| Flower         | azalea    | marigold | balloon-flower | zinnia |

