.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, azalea, dahlia
House: cape-cod, palace, farmhouse, townhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the farmhouse house is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the palace house is the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growsdahlia##2
9. the person who growsazalea is between the person eating lemon and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Flower       | iris   | sunflower   | azalea | dahlia |
| House         | cape-cod   | farmhouse | townhouse       | palace    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

