.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, sunflower, marigold
House: cottage, art-deco, cape-cod, craftsman
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
 2. the craftsman house is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the craftsman house is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the art-deco house is the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the cottage house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the owner of the bird and the person who growsmarigold##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | begonia  | marigold | balloon-flower     | sunflower |
| House   | craftsman | cottage  | cape-cod | art-deco       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

