.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann, swisher, cain
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, pop, hip-hop, indie
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 8. the fan of pop is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar          | dannemann         | swisher         | aristoff     | cain      |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop | indie | trance    | pop     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

