The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, aconite, amaryllis
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the car##2
2. the freelancer is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the person who growsaconite is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who growsaconite is the person who growsaconite##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Transport   | taxi      | motorbike       | snowmobile     | car      |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | balloon-flower      | aconite   | orchid   |
