There 4 different types of food: zucchini, pepper, potato, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 2. the palace house is the dutch##1
 3. the person eating pepper is between the dutch and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the person eating potato is the person driving the train##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the modern house##1
 6. the palace house is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the argentine is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
 9. the palace house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
10. the dutch is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House   | craftsman | palace | farmhouse  | modern  |
| Food   | zucchini       | potato   | pepper | pomegranate    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

