3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of soul##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who likes aquamarine##2
6. the fan of electronic is the person who likes emerald##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
