.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, animation, adventure
 1. the person drinking juice is the fisherman##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the fisherman is the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person watching spy movies##2
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | iced-tea        | milk    | almond-milk | juice   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation       | adventure | spy    | zombie  |

