The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | crime    | documentary      | musical |
| Birthday       | june        | march       | april       | may     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

